Use Case
	Steer ship
Actors
	User, system, ship
Description
	The user holds down a key representing movement. 
	The system reads the key. The system steers the ship
Main Course of Events
Actor			System								Ship
1.Presses key
				2.Read key
 				3.Check if key represents steering
 													4.Change ship heading
Alternative Flow of Events
2.1 Wrong key. No change in system